{"tid":1817962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港眾志組織幹事黃莉莉於機場被捕 或涉「7.1佔領立法會」事件","createTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T15:06:53.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"42dbca2be665b123e0216b1e235b6402740e2984","tid":1817962,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"香港眾志組織幹事黃莉莉，原定於今日傍晚乘班機到台灣，參觀當地選舉活動。<br />\n<br />\n惟離境期間被帶走，並證實被警方以「串謀刑事毀壞」罪名拘捕，或涉「7.1佔領立法會」事件。<br />\n<br />\n協助跟進的律師表示，過去一段時間黃莉莉都被警方列作「通緝人士」，然而當事人在今天之前並不知情。香港眾志呼籲所有行動者注意警方於出入境期間「突襲」拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1ntjCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1ntjCJ.jpg&h=c224850d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/photos/a.497376730471154/1314198845455601/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fphotos%2Fa.497376730471154%2F1314198845455601%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF07e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=9e9af190\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/photos/a.497376730471154/1314198845455601/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"7aec6357747118de3139d1266a982fcdffffc31c","tid":1817962,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a023d3355d1ef7e67eb571a68262abcab424ba7b","tid":1817962,"uid":198783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"又低調通緝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160285e46e7dc8b9c6d5f838e8f14918236fc310","tid":1817962,"uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13: